name: DistantCoder
printed_effect:
When you Cast this DistantCoder you can Enchant
up to {omni}{omni}{omni} to it. When an Elestral declares an
attack you can Disenchant {omni} from this DistantCoder
with the same Element as a Spirit Enchanting that
Elestral in order to Negate that attack.
effect: When you Cast this DistantCoder you can Enchant up to {omni}{omni}{omni} to it. When an Elestral declares an attack you can Disenchant a Spirit from this DistantCoder of the same Element as a Spirit Enchanting that Elestral in order to Negate that attack.
